<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - 查無網頁</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style3.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 背景裝飾 -->
    <div class="background-shapes">
        <div class="shape shape1"></div>
        <div class="shape shape2"></div>
        <div class="shape shape3"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="error-code">404</div>

        <h1 class="error-title">查無此網頁</h1>

        <p class="error-message">
            抱歉，您所訪問的頁面不存在或已被移除
        </p>

        <p class="error-submessage">
            The page you are looking for might have been removed, had its name changed, or is temporarily unavailable.
        </p>

        <div class="error-actions">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
                <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
                返回首頁
            </a>
            <a href="/calculator" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i>
                貸款計算器
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="error-suggestions">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> 可能的原因：</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>網址輸入錯誤，請檢查拼字</li>
                <li>該頁面已經被刪除或移動</li>
                <li>連結已過期或失效</li>
                <li>您沒有權限訪問此頁面</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 自動記錄錯誤訪問
        console.log('404 Error: Page not found - ' + window.location.href);

        // 可選：3秒後自動返回首頁（取消註解以啟用）
        // setTimeout(() => {
        //     window.location.href = 'index.html';
        // }, 3000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
